a dime is a 10year term tuesday night frank had been 
alerted and is nowhere to be found his thirdfloor apartment is 
dark 
well be patient says elithorpe tomorrow next week next 
month frank will turn up 
dressed in jeans and sweatshirts elithorpe and his partner for 
the night sherzan try to keep on an increasingly hectic schedule 
that schedule means gangs as well as drugs 
it looks like were entering vice lord land south of here is 
the crips said elithorpe they stake it out and let it be 
known it isnt healthy to compete 
theyre looking for jim whos done time for selling drugs and 
runs many of the prostitutes up and down the street pulling up 
next to a patrol car they hail a uniformed officer 
have you seen jim asks elithorpe 
jim i just sent him up the officer replies 
hes back 
did i waste my time or what groans the officer 
iowas image is usually idyllic like that portrayed in the 
movie field of dreams 
with a rebounding state economy and jobs to be found there are 
few of the pressures that plague other cities there is however 
crack 
its a field of dreams for a few said sherzan yes its 
getting worse why its crack cocaine youre looking at a county 
with a 3 percent unemployment rate its not jobs 
on the streets some residents fight back others hunker down 
people are getting sick of it said sherzan on a good 
summer night youll see 50 or 100 people up and down this street 
taking part in a neighborhood patrol 
but a few blocks away outside a tavern crowds gather and crack 
is traded openly its a freefire zone elithorpe said 
on the citys near north side sits homes of oakridge a public 
housing project that drug czar william bennett will tour next 
month the brightly colored brick buildings dont have the 
bombedout look of projects in other cities but they house many of 
the same problems 
cesar lives there or he did his drug of choice is alcohol and 
theres a warrant with his name also he had the bad luck to be 
home when elithorpe knocked and he wont be around for bennetts 
visit 
his mother watches quietly her head hung the scene isnt new 
in this tiny apartment 
as the shift ends elithorpe brightens 
lets do this again he said we do this all the time 
