that 43 billion of the money appropriated for the defense 
department in the fiscal year beginning sunday be spent on star 
wars 
on tuesday the senate had voted overwhelmingly 6634 to spend 
37 billion on star wars formally known as the strategic defense 
initiative and lawmakers indicated that the vote reflected an 
erosion in the support for the program 
but the ranking members of the senate armed services committee 
