administration into indicating the future of the program and what 
level of funding it will accept 
the administration has to put a line in the sand on what is 
not acceptable to them i hope this shakes the administration out 
of its unwillingness to confront this issue in a sharp way he 
said 
every year theyre losing more support they dont have any 
program or any plan he said 
