demonstrators sign paraphrasing bushs widely quoted opposition 
to raising taxes 
democratic governors meanwhile played down the issue of 
increased federal school aid although they warned that washington 
ultimately must bolster its support for public education 
we just dont think that at this time its worth letting the 
summit break apart over a fight over how much money theyll have to 
