differences could be resolved 
he said an interfaith symposium should be convened to discuss 
problems 
we want the jews to understand us especially the jews in 
america who talk a lot but do not understand the situation we 
want them to develop a correct respect for the poles the 
newspaper quoted glemp as saying 
