on friday the spokesman said 
the visit marks another in the series of highlevel ussoviet 
military exchanges that have occurred amid the warming of 
superpower relations 
yazov and former defense secretary frank carlucci met last year 
in switzerland in sessions that led to an exchange of visits 
between the chairman of the joint chiefs of staff adm william 
crowe jr and his counterpart gen sergei akromeyev to each 
others homelands 
the defense ministers visit to the united states reciprocates a 
visit carlucci made to the soviet union in august 1988 
yazov is to be greeted at the pentagon on monday with a full 
honors ceremony by defense secretary dick cheney 
