curt carlson was a salesman in 1938 in 1988 he 
sat atop an almost fully owned personally assembled empire with 
sales of more than 53 billion a year one of the biggest 
companies in america 
today in minnetonka minn he steps away from daytoday 
operations of carlson companies inc employer of 55000 people 
