the commission also challenged claims that the product offers 
all of fibers wonderful health benefits and provides 235 
grams of fiber in one serving 
the panel voted 40 to issue the complaint with chairwoman 
janet steiger not voting the ftc has set a nov 28 hearing date 
schering corp a subsidiary of scheringplough corp a major 
national pharmaceutical manufacturer is the us distributor of 
fibre trim 
fibre trim sold as a diet pill and fruit tablets to be 
dissolved in water is manufactured in denmark 
we believe the advertising for fibre trim was completely 
truthful and properly substantiated said steve galpin a 
schering spokesman 
six strictly controlled studies in which some patients were 
given placebos demonstrate the effectiveness of fibre trim 
galpin said 
he also said there was an extensive body of scientific 
literature showing that fiber can be used to help people lose 
weight 
