subsidiary on its fundamental patents for portable laptop computers 
the most notable of the patents are those for tandys new 
gridpad which is the first pc designed to address applications 
such as utility meter reading census taking and inventory order 
taking where data must be gathered or forms filled out while 
standing or walking 
